descriptionNullable:
This dataset was collected from a Dionaea Honeypot hosted in AWS us-west-1 region (North California). 

The data spans between 05/07/2022 and 05/08/2022. 
There were 27,574 connections to the honeypot recorded. 

While this is a honeypot, some connections may be from "mass scanners" and other security researchers. 
However, no domain name was given to the public IP address. 

The following features were captured:

1. Protocol - the protocol of the connection made, such as "smbd"
2. Transport - the transport protocol used, such as "tcp"
3. Type
4. dst_port - Destination Port
5. src_ip - Source IP
6. src_port - Source Port
7. timestamp
title: Cybersecurity Honeypot Attacks
subtitle: Real Cyber Attack Data
